<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>snyn ṭwylẗ mḍt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (snyn ṭwylẗ mḍt .. wạlrb mʿtny by
 wkl ywm mḥmwl .. ʿ ạlạ̉dẖrʿ ạlạ̉bdyẗ)2
 (wyswʿ bydh mạskny .. fy mrạʿy ạlḥb qạydny)2
 2- (mlk ạlmlwk yạ yswʿ .. yạ syd ạlạ̉syạd
 nfwsnạ fy ạntẓạr .. tạkẖdẖnạ llạ̉mjạd)2
 (wạtmly̱ fyk bʿynyã .. yạ yswʿ yạ gẖạly ʿlyã)2
 3- (yswʿ sbạny bḥbh .. wạlqlb bqy frḥạn
 wʿd yyjynạ mn mjdh .. wtnthy ạlạ̉ḥzạn)2
 (tbqy̱ ạlsmạ klhạ lyã .. wạ̉ʿẓm mạ fyhạ fạdyã)2</lyrics>
